137629047165312759.Text: I found a Redguard trader in Nammu named Jon Hawker. He had been taken prisoner by a battlemage named Galmis Dren, to be sold as a slave. He had prayed to the Nine for aid, and thought I was the answer to his prayers. He asked for a Divine Intervention scroll, so he could escape, but I didn't have any. He suggested that he had some Divine Intervention scrolls when he was captured, and that they might be around somewhere.

210412859139614537.Text: I found a Redguard trader in Nammu named Jon Hawker. He had been taken prisoner by a battlemage named Galmis Dren, to be sold as a slave. He had prayed to the Nine for aid, and thought I was the answer to his prayers. I gave him a Divine Intervention scroll and he disappeared, but he gave me two gifts. It is strange -- such valuable gifts. How did he hide them from Galmis Dren?
